data.description: Built in 2017, this Richmond American Home is beautifully laid out, 4 bedrooms, Loft, Plus Den with double doors, plenty of living space & stunning sunset views. Walk into your front Living Room, Open to the Kitchen with granite counters, new appliances, huge walk in pantry, huge family room with tile flooring downstairs. Your den can be a guest bedroom or office downstairs. Upstairs you have 3 guest bedrooms, large dual vanity bathroom, huge loft with storage. The Master suite has a spacious bathroom, dual vanity, separate tub and shower, enclosed toilet room, and huge walk in closet. Stunning Views out your backyard of the Arizona Sunsets, a view fence and desert behind the home. Community park, playground, & basketball court down the street! Current VA loan at 2.49% could be Assumable!
